pageProduct.name: Swisse Skincare Argan Youthful Facial Oil 50ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

With Vitamin E, Ferulic Acid and Omegas 6 and 9

Swisse Argan Youthful Facial Oil features Certified Organic Argan Oil which is scientifically proven to be rich in antioxidant compounds such as Vitamin E, Ferulic Acid and Omegas 6 and 9, to protect the skin from environmental damage and prevent premature aging.

Suitable For: All skin types

Warnings

Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner.

Ingredients

ARGAN OIL Certified Organic Argania Spinosa Kernel (Argan) Oil
Argania Spinosa Kernel (Argan) Oil
Tocopherol (Vitamin E derived from Soy and Sunflower)
GRAPEFRUIT Citrus Paradisi (Grapefruit) Peel Oil
ORANGE Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Peel Oil
Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) Oil
MAY CHANG Litsea Cubeba Fruit (May Chang) Oil
ROSE GERANIUM Pelargonium Graveolens Flower (Rose Geranium) Oil
Fragrance

Directions

Gently massage 2-3 drops into clean, dry skin until absorbed. This product contains essential oils.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store upright below 28°C.
